{% do view.registerAssetBundle("cavellblood\\sunsettosunset\\assetbundles\\sunsettosunset\\SunsetToSunsetAsset") %}
<div class="sts-container  {{ bannerCssPosition == 'fixed' ? 'sts-container--fixed' }}"
     style="
     {{ bannerCssPosition ? 'position: ' ~ bannerCssPosition ~ ';' }}
		{{ bannerCssBackgroundColor ? 'background-color: ' ~ bannerCssBackgroundColor ~ ';' }}
             "
>
    <div class="sts-message">
        <p>
            {{ bannerMessage }}
            The store will be closed from
            <strong>
                <time datetime="{{ closingTime | date('c') }}">{{ closingTime | date('l, F j \\a\\t g:ia T') }}</time>
            </strong>
            and will re-open on
            <strong>
                <time datetime="{{ openingTime | date('c') }}">{{ openingTime | date('l, F j \\a\\t g:ia T') }}</time>.
            </strong>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>